        <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">Mais de 20 subcomandos: <code>run</code>, <code>build</code> (JS/Wasm), <code>test</code>, <code>repl</code>, <code>format</code>, <code>docs</code>, <code>lsp</code>, <code>init</code>, <code>install</code>, <code>publish</code>, <code>watch</code>, <code>benchmark</code>. Bin&aacute;rio &uacute;nico via <code>bun --compile</code>, zero depend&ecirc;ncias em tempo de execu&ccedil;&atilde;o.</p>
