        <h3 class="font-bold text-base sm:text-lg mb-2">Executor de Tarefas</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">Declara&ccedil;&otilde;es <code>TAREFA</code> em <code>tarefas.xs</code> definem tarefas nomeadas analisadas em AST. Executadas via <code>xs &lt;taskname&gt;</code> com resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o de depend&ecirc;ncias.</p>
